Description: Computing package for Multidimensional Poverty Index (MPI) using Alkire-Foster method. Please see "Alkire, S., Foster, J. E., Seth, S., Santos, M. E., Roche, J. M., and Ballon, P. (2015). Multidimensional Poverty Measurement and Analysis, Oxford: Oxford University Press, ch. 5." for The Alkire-Foster methodology.
